OL,5, Some of the poorest households in      
OL,6, England and Wales are struggling to    
OL,7, access council tax rebates to help     
OL,8, offset their soaring energy bills, a   
OL,9, charity has warned.                    
OL,11,FNational Energy Action said those who  
OL,12,Fdid not pay council tax by direct debit
OL,13,Fwere affected, with many facing long   
OL,14,Fwaits for the #150 payouts.            
OL,16,FCouncils say they are struggling to    
OL,17,Fadminister the rebates at short notice.
OL,19,FBut the government said they should    
OL,20,Fmake the payouts without further delay.
